      "acceptanceCriteria": "The validated QoI (RH, shear stress) must be directly linked to the clinical decision metric (device hemolysis classification).",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory metric for CPB device comparison. Shear stress is the mechanistic driver of red cell damage in the power-law hemolysis model. Both QoIs are directly relevant to the COU decision."
