    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates RH < 1 at all five COU operating points with normalised RMSE of 0.063. The uncertainty quantification campaign (MOR-UQ-2024-01) confirms that input and geometric uncertainties do not challenge the acceptance criterion. The credibility assessment team unanimously accepts the CFD model as fit for purpose for the stated COU.",
